{"tid":1052260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[利害了我的蟈]海關總署：中國對美貿易順差再擴大3.9%","createTime":"2019-03-08T07:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T08:03:03.000Z","uid":121058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a0d47d14b6dc02e9859dbc0a3b740cfb60dded","tid":1052260,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:34:15.000Z","msg":"[東網報導]中國海關總署周五（8日）公布最新貿易數據，今年首兩個月，中國對美國貿易順差2,900.9億元（人民幣‧下同，約3423億港元），擴大3.9%；對美國的進出口均有下跌。另外，這兩個月中國共進口大豆1,183萬噸，按年跌14.9%。<br />\n據海關統計，本年1月及2月中國貨物貿易進出口總值4.54萬億元（約5.35萬億港元），同比增長0.7%；對美出口4075.3億元（4808億港元），下跌9.9%；自美國進口1174.4億元（約1386億港元），下降32.2%。<br />\n首兩個月合計，原油進口8,182萬噸，增長12.4%。成品油進口572萬噸，增長4.4%。天然氣進口1,736萬噸，增長18.5%<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190308/bkn-20190308133421499-0308_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190308%2Fbkn-20190308133421499-0308_00952_001.html&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMoVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=89bfe0da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190308/bkn-20190308133421499-0308_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"30fb1f0f49b08462239276994be2c409c2667e03","tid":1052260,"uid":121058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:39:14.000Z","msg":"[華爾街日報]中國2月出口同比大跌，貿易順差僅41.2億美元<br />\n中國海關總署周五公布的數據顯示，2月份貿易數據全面走低。以美元計，2月份中國出口同比下跌20.7%，進口同比下降5.2%，貿易順差收窄至僅41.2億美元。<br />\n中國海關總署周五公布的數據顯示，2月份中國外貿數據大幅下滑，扭轉了1月份走高向好的態勢。<br />\n海關公布，以美元計，2月份中國出口同比下跌20.7%，進口同比下降5.2%，貿易帳為順差41.2億美元，收窄87.2%。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母啦東網 壞新聞都可以搵到角度打飛機<br />\n人地公布二月數據 你加埋一月一齊計<br />\n唔講咁多 強蟈又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UzAVvAS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUzAVvAS.jpg&h=a467f1cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf627bbf620a7dcffd1befde380239338a076798","tid":1052260,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f0c1ffab76b8f78d67d9dcfd72a625b8e12415","tid":1052260,"uid":29874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30fb1f0f49b08462239276994be2c409c2667e03","tid":1052260,"uid":121058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:39:14.000Z","msg":"[華爾街日報]中國2月出口同比大跌，貿易順差僅41.2億美元<br />\n中國海關總署周五公布的數據顯示，2月份貿易數據全面走低。以美元計，2月份中國出口同比下跌20.7%，進口同比下降5.2%，貿易順差收窄至僅41.2億美元。<br />\n中國海關總署周五公布的數據顯示，2月份中國外貿數據大幅下滑，扭轉了1月份走高向好的態勢。<br />\n海關公布，以美元計，2月份中國出口同比下跌20.7%，進口同比下降5.2%，貿易帳為順差41.2億美元，收窄87.2%。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母啦東網 壞新聞都可以搵到角度打飛機<br />\n人地公布二月數據 你加埋一月一齊計<br />\n唔講咁多 強蟈又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UzAVvAS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUzAVvAS.jpg&h=a467f1cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:01:12.000Z","msg":"而家支那唔俾出負面新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢咁出咪俾啲聰明人知要睇路，走得好走，蠢嘅咪繼續留係到打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374a7afeda95cd3db449ffe040675880be2dd814","tid":1052260,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01f0c1ffab76b8f78d67d9dcfd72a625b8e12415","tid":1052260,"uid":29874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30fb1f0f49b08462239276994be2c409c2667e03","tid":1052260,"uid":121058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:39:14.000Z","msg":"[華爾街日報]中國2月出口同比大跌，貿